snippet.title: Bay Area Buggs
snippet.description:
Welcome!
My channel is primarily gaming, I started my channel with GTA 4 and a mod called LCPDFR. I have since expanded my channel to not just one game but multiple games. I currently play GTA 5 Role-Play the most. I will continue to play more & more games and hopefully you will join me!

►Channel Art▼
All Art Was Created by Tommy Rios
Tommy's Website: http://battletr.wix.com/officialriosdesigns
